749
01:18:37,000 --> 01:18:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nekako i se ispucaš naš kvalitetno, kad si umora nakon treninga onda imaš dojam nekog postignuća.

750
01:18:45,000 --> 01:18:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta voliš mjesto?

751
01:18:48,000 --> 01:18:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta volim mjesto?

752
01:18:50,000 --> 01:18:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pitaj me šta ne volim mjesto?

753
01:18:52,000 --> 01:18:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je, to je, ali mislim šta ima, ne.

754
01:18:56,000 --> 01:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ima, evo, to i jedem, realno.

755
01:18:58,000 --> 01:19:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisi izbirljiv?

756
01:19:00,000 --> 01:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, realno, ne.

757
01:19:02,000 --> 01:19:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

758
01:19:04,000 --> 01:19:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da jedino što ne prolazi je hladitina, evo, to.

759
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:10,000
