766
01:19:21,000 --> 01:19:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ovo.

767
01:19:22,000 --> 01:19:23,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tri pica.

768
01:19:23,000 --> 01:19:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] To, to.

769
01:19:24,000 --> 01:19:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa, moramo ja iti ići na to pivo.

770
01:19:28,000 --> 01:19:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možem.

771
01:19:29,000 --> 01:19:31,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja samo gledam na sad.

772
01:19:31,000 --> 01:19:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] A vidim ja da usta ti se osušila, popio si dvije čaše vode i sad ne pivo.

773
01:19:36,000 --> 01:19:38,000
